**PipelineStepHandler** (two-layer interface):

```typescript
// Base — engine/step-runner.ts
interface PipelineStepHandler {
  readonly stepType: StepType;
  execute(config: Record<string, unknown>, context: ExecutionContext): Promise<StepResult>;
}

// Enriched — steps/interface.ts (extends above)
interface PipelineStepHandler extends EngineStepHandler {
  validateConfig(config: Record<string, unknown>): string[];
}
```

**ExecutionContext** (engine/step-runner.ts):
```typescript
interface ExecutionContext {
  tenantId: string;
  executionId: string;
  pipelineId: string;
